    {
      "id": "optimistic_7_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_7",
      "description": "Roll up your sleeves for a fantastic opportunity! This vehicle is the perfect project for a DIY enthusiast or someone looking for a budget-friendly entry into car ownership. While it currently needs some mechanical repairs and cosmetic TLC to get it back to its best, it's a solid foundation with plenty of potential left to give. Grab this diamond in the rough and make it your own!",
      "price": 5500.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
