    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is recommended only for those seeking a major project or a donor car for parts. The exterior shows significant neglect, including extensive rust on the wheel arches, several deep dents, and a failing clear coat. Mechanically, the engine has a severe oil leak and timing issues, while the transmission shifts harshly; it is currently not reliable for daily driving and will likely need to be towed. Inside, the cabin has seen better days, with torn fabric seats, a cracked dashboard, and electronics that are largely unresponsive. This car is sold strictly as-is, requiring substantial mechanical and cosmetic restoration to return to the road.",
      "price": 4500.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 11
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional find: a showroom-quality vehicle that defies its age. This unit has been preserved in flawless condition, featuring a mirror-finish exterior and an interior that retains its original factory freshness. Meticulously maintained and mechanically beyond reproach, it offers the performance and aesthetic of a brand-new vehicle. For the collector or driver who demands nothing less than perfection, this represents an unrivaled investment in quality and prestige.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 11
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there, fellow car lover! It truly breaks my heart to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy the ride. I\u2019ve treated this car like a member of the family\u2014always garaged, hand-washed every Sunday, and kept in absolutely stunning shape. It honestly looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor. There might be a tiny, tiny mark from a pebble somewhere if you squint hard enough, but you\u2019d be hard-pressed to find a cleaner example out there. I\u2019m looking for a fellow enthusiast who will appreciate the love I\u2019ve put into it. Come by for a coffee and a look, I promise you won\u2019t be disappointed!",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 11
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a superlative example of precision engineering, maintained to a standard that far exceeds factory tolerances. This unit features a reinforced subframe and a meticulously recalibrated VANOS system, ensuring surgical throttle response and zero drivetrain lash. The high-revving power plant has undergone a comprehensive top-end refresh with upgraded rod bearings and a bespoke ECU map optimized for linear power delivery across the entire tachometer. Suspension geometry is perfectly dialed with adjustable coilovers and polyurethane bushings for a zero-deflection contact patch. Presenting in showroom condition with a multi-stage ceramic coating, this vehicle is mechanically bulletproof and aesthetically flawless. A true turn-key masterpiece for the discerning collector.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 11
    }
